      "content": "i know i should seek help or whatever, but it just feels so pointless. like, what's the point of fixing a person that doesn't even exist anymore? people only cared about the \"perfect\" me. now that i've failed so publicly, there's nothing left to salvage. it feels more real than anything else right now... the idea that the person i used to be is just... gone. like, truly gone.",
